---
title: Double Asian Edamame Veggie Dumpling Broth with Sweetcorn & Spring Onion
description: A dumpling soup is something to get excited about for two reasons. First, it’s super easy to make by cooking all the
veggies and dumplings then simply adding them to the soup. Second, it’s a dumpling soup, isn’t that reason enough to give three cheers?

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
